#. Tag: title
#: whatsnew.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bug fixes and enhancements to functionality"
msgstr "Correcções de erros e melhorias na funcionalidade"

#. Tag: para
#: whatsnew.docbook:10
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "As with every release, the &kmymoney; development team continues to work "
#| "hard to make each version better and easier to use in every way. This is "
#| "the third release in the 5.1 series, and most of the activity has been "
#| "directed to fixing bugs."
msgid ""
"As with every release, the &kmymoney; development team continues to work "
"hard to make each version better and easier to use in every way. Many bugs "
"have been fixed since the previous stable release of 5.1.3; several areas of "
"the program have seen functional enhancements; but the major noticeable "
"changes from the 5.1 series of releases are in the ledger - more details "
"below."
msgstr ""
"Como em todas as versões, a equipa de desenvolvimento do &kmymoney; tentou "
"ao máximo tornar esta versão melhor e mais simples de usar de todas as "
"formas. Esta é a quarta versão na série 5.1, e a maior parte da actividade "
"decorrida foi direccionada para a correcção de erros."

#. Tag: para
#: whatsnew.docbook:18
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "As of 5.1, the conversion to using &kde-frameworks; is essentially "
#| "complete, although that and the work to update many of the underlying "
#| "libraries used by the application are behind the scenes and not directly "
#| "visible to the end user. The general look and feel should be stable, "
#| "although some minor changes may still occur. The basic functionality of "
#| "the program also remains the same, aside from intentional improvements "
#| "and additions."
msgid ""
"The conversion from using the earlier &kde; libraries to &kde-frameworks; "
"was essentially complete in the early 5.1.x releases, with much of that work "
"behind the scenes and not directly visible to the end user. The general look "
"and feel should continue to remain stable, although some minor changes may "
"be noticeable. In addition, the team has begun to make changes to support "
"the conversion to using Qt6 and KDE6 libraries, which have already started "
"to replace Qt5 and KDE5. With all these changes, the basic functionality of "
"the program remains the same, aside from intentional bug fixes, "
"improvements, and additions."
msgstr ""
"Nesta altura, a conversão para as &kde-frameworks; está quase completa, mas "
"a maior parte disso está nos bastidores, não sendo visível para o utilizador "
"final. A aparência e comportamento gerais mantiveram-se mais ou menos "
"estáveis, mas ainda algumas coisas pequenas poderão ter mudado. A "
"funcionalidade básica do programa mantém-se igual, à parte de algumas "
"melhorias e adições intencionais."

#. Tag: para
#: whatsnew.docbook:29
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In past releases, this page of the manual has included a list of many of "
#| "the specific bug fixes and functional enhancements. However, rather than "
#| "duplicating that information, you can find it directly in the <ulink url="
#| "\"https://kmymoney.org/changelog.html\">Changelog</ulink>."
msgid ""
"In past releases, this section of the manual included a list of many of the "
"specific bug fixes and functional enhancements. However, rather than "
"duplicating that information, you can find it directly in the <ulink url="
"\"https://kmymoney.org/changelog.html\">Changelog</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Nas últimas versões, esta página do manual incluiu uma lista de diversas "
"correcções de erros e melhorias funcionais. Contudo, em vez de duplicar esta "
"informação, podê-la-á encontrar directamente nas <ulink url=\"https://"
"kmymoney.org/changelog.html\">Notas de Lançamento</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: whatsnew.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The 5.0.x and 5.1.x series included some changes needing adjustments on the "
"user's side, if they were upgrading from 4.8.x or an older version. However, "
"we expect that most users have converted to 5.1.x by now. Specifically, "
"there should be no adjustments needed by users converting from 5.1.x to 5.2. "
"If for some reason, you are still using &kmymoney; version 4, you are very "
"strongly encouraged to upgrade, as it is getting increasingly difficult for "
"the team to provide any assistance for very old versions."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: whatsnew.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Updates to this Handbook"
msgstr "Actualizações Neste Manual"

#. Tag: para
#: whatsnew.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section used to present some details related to the lack of a complete "
"handbook update from 4.x to 5.x. As the handbook has now been fully updated "
"for 5.2, this section is no longer necessary."
msgstr ""

#~ msgid "2019-04-04"
#~ msgstr "2019-04-04"

#~ msgid "5.0.4"
#~ msgstr "5.0.4"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Since the release of 5.0, there have been some changes which will need "
#~ "adjustments on the user's side if you are upgrading from 4.8.x or an "
#~ "older version. However, we expect that most users have converted to 5.x "
#~ "by now."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Desde o lançamento do 5.0, existem algumas alterações que irão necessitar "
#~ "de alguns ajustes do lado do utilizador, caso esteja a actualizar a "
#~ "partir da versão 4.8.x ou de outra versão anterior. Contudo, contamos que "
#~ "a maioria dos utilizadores já tenha migrado para a 5.x nesta altura."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "For some time now, the program searches for the templates for the "
#~ "printcheck plugin in different locations than previously. If this is "
#~ "still an issue for you, you need to account for this in the plugins "
#~ "setting dialog, <link linkend=\"details.settings.plugins\">see this "
#~ "section for more details</link>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Já há algum tempo, o programa procura pelos modelos, no 'plugin' de "
#~ "impressão de cheques, em locais diferentes. O utilizador precisa de ter "
#~ "isto em conta na janela de configuração dos 'plugins'; <link linkend="
#~ "\"details.settings.plugins\">veja esta secção para saber mais detalhes</"
#~ "link>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "While we continue to make progress, there are still chapters of this "
#~ "handbook which have not been updated to reflect all changes in the "
#~ "program which are visible to the user as of 5.0. Each chapter does "
#~ "identify the release of &kmymoney; for which it was last updated, but we "
#~ "present the complete list here, as a quick reference."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Embora continuemos a progredir, existem ainda capítulos deste manual que "
#~ "possam não ter sido actualizados para reflectir todas as alterações no "
#~ "programa que são visíveis para o utilizador desde a versão 5.0. Cada "
#~ "capítulo identifica de facto a versão do &kmymoney; para a qual foi "
#~ "actualizado da última vez, mas apresentamos à mesma aqui a lista completa "
#~ "para referência rápida."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "However, please note that extent to which the chapters which have not "
#~ "been explicitly updated do or do not reflect the current operation of the "
#~ "program depends on how much that area of the program has changed between "
#~ "the 4.8 and the 5.0 and 5.1 releases."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Contudo, lembre-se do âmbito em que os capítulos possam não ter sido "
#~ "actualizados pode reflectir ou não a operação actual do programa, "
#~ "dependendo da quantidade de alterações nesse programa entre as versões "
#~ "4.8 e 5.0 ou 5.1."

